{"tid":1632073,"cid":33,"subCid":0,"title":"手足覺得裝修對政權傷害大啲？定民主法案大啲？","createTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","updateTime":"2019-10-06T17:48:54.000Z","uid":82520,"like":10,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":13,"replies":[{"pid":"3e89eaea5c58527afba30f15913f38ead8024e7c","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:18.000Z","msg":"講真，我都完全唔想再開多個呢啲post<br />\n首先我想講我不割席不分化<br />\n但係要反省同改善<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/sowhat.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n回應返標題，下面個post都講得好足<br />\n<br />\n勇武退場，美軍來了！<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1631477\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1631477</a><br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n可以係個標題改得唔好今人覺得有分化feel<br />\n但唔好唔記得民主法案先係真正核彈<br />\n大家記唔記得我地想條法案通過幾耐？<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/wail.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n記唔記得呢條法案嘅聽證會？<br />\n當外國有輿論對我地不利，前線係咪真係可以唔理？<br />\n事後文宣做得幾多？<br />\n裝修除左要文宣解釋同時亦會被敵人無限放大。<br />\n<br />\n為此，希望前線可以遵從黑<span style=\"color: red;\">紅</span><span style=\"color: blue;\">藍</span><span style=\"color: gold;\">黃</span>原則<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/arrested.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n話唔要教條主義，不要原則嘅人<br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\">當你搞美心吉野家仲落力過政府同民建聯建築你唔會有少少疑問？</span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n勇氣與智慧永不滅<br />\n有勇，都要用腦<br />\n每日反省可以點做得更好<br />\n做人冇公關 食屎㗎啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e8f08aebce0088235b71cd167aec32dfd23b4760","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:30.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"a927ff038a4d9c31602ebf9b1425a7ac24b3ff36","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:43.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"da76fe2dd098719cebfc45f9edf49f2e91c7e6c7","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:56:53.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"200d905bfac34f486e2be58ce11cbdd75f2c1b94","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:03.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"602ba33e88e0b1d33c150da6bfcae3774538c967","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:13.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"ed939465f8314c8afadd651067d2fd093f1042a6","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:23.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"c289ce8a548efa9b9564ea976d7eca32748e85b8","tid":1632073,"uid":130079,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:26.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"color: gold;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">係外國既香港人都可以一齊係連登出力！</span></strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n【重開】［眾籌俾連登］開一個英文版面俾連登仔<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630849\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630849</a><br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/1630201\" target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/1630201</a><br />\n<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n現時連登急需亦好要一個<span style=\"color: gold;\"><span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">英文台/或者係新既英文介面，全部台都有英文版咁。</span></span><br />\n<br />\n主要用途係對外文宣用，如果個論壇冧左，<span style=\"color: purple;\">外國人更加清楚lihkg被攻擊同香港自由被剝既嚴重性</span>。<br />\n<br />\ntwitter有lihkg,reddit開post<br />\n但始終都唔係lihkg開英文台<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n好處：<br />\n1.連登多左流覽量，廣告費多左<br />\n2.同上，每次被攻擊都睇到香港無自由，the world is watching<br />\n3.理論上少風向文宣，因為如果要落手帶風向，對家就要大學畢業既人，文宣戰立即少左散仔協會參戰，但香港市民最多就係呢一堆人。<br />\n4.<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><strong><span style=\"color: gold;\">外國巴打可以幫手文宣，尤其exchange學生，仲可以介紹俾其他國家既人</span></strong></span><br />\n5.擴大和理非平台，快速文宣，一個巴絲可翻譯，另一巴絲亦可做搬運工，快速輸出文宣<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n大家如果見到既<br />\n幫手：<br />\n1.<span style=\"color: red;\">幫推，唔該3連推一次</span><br />\n2.連登search其他 英文台 國際台，<span style=\"color: green;\">將入面相關要求既post再推</span><br />\n<br />\n3.share link去fb tg，叫其他有account既人入黎再一齊做返1同2<br />\n4.<span style=\"color: orange;\">堅持每日全部post再一推</span><br />\n5.Fb 連登到留comment，叫連仔開英文台<br />\n6. Fb進行洗版式接龍活動，令到連仔開到/知道要開英文台為止<br />\n7.太舊既post只可以推番三個上水，幫手推埋thx<br />\n<br />\n如果你係要求開英文台post樓主既：<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">集中連推自己所有既英文台post，我會幫推，唔好放棄推<br />\n</span></span>"},{"pid":"df141b841a57890c7959dd31cda9848e3986dba7","tid":1632073,"uid":133728,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/jYtuLaR.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FjYtuLaR.jpg&h=f5ef1ebb&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"27828286ab6df683ba33cbc0d1bea2ca0e2e6d8e","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:33.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"29d2c1e0f34c590df407997f7740b5dece3fa5ad","tid":1632073,"uid":258572,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:36.000Z","msg":"push"},{"pid":"8c48b2630d98307d2a91ab7054c0f218aad2ebd9","tid":1632073,"uid":7343,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:57:50.000Z","msg":"Magnisky act"},{"pid":"4514d4df38b9c1a2e7024c62c579c48a338ad35f","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:58:31.000Z","msg":"大家一齊討論下<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n有咩人可以制裁得大力過美國"},{"pid":"53c197f9c3c91514dcb31393dce52e65ff6dd8f4","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T16:59:55.000Z","msg":"我甚至覺得應該要嚟多次美領集會"},{"pid":"b94955620cee15c46cb656b7f04bcae656a2925b","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:06.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d946404c942d81abf708c2c94e185c5fac17bcc9","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:32.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"2ab4c8f86efd189e81a5387a5223bcaf253dddc5","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:00:53.000Z","msg":"同意嘅幫得推一推"},{"pid":"6c033020ec55d6e1749cfb35a43b639239125438","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:01:16.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"d9f9c60c4b6bcca9377a958238a55a7435e14309","tid":1632073,"uid":123969,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:04.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"192a7b905a37323f2b57b2a8ba5da1b510b8f641","tid":1632073,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 美國佬係唔會因為你爆幾塊玻璃而唔過法案 全部都係中美博弈黎 佢要過你殺埋警都一樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"6ee998bbc55e2140e2d3e9e9285ec7d4a88a4506","tid":1632073,"uid":280492,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:04:54.000Z","msg":"同意，通過法案既威力更會激起其他國家對香港既關注，我地應該製造d好d既主題比外國傳媒寫，而家佢地見到le幾日既情況大多以總結為&quot;商鋪，交通，被示威者破壞&quot;，縱然我地知道每一個被破壞既都有佢背後原因，但外國，even 香港大多數人，佢地都唔好深究"},{"pid":"0e8c1e91429f3eb2155d6dcf68af2b83c2c395d9","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192a7b905a37323f2b57b2a8ba5da1b510b8f641","tid":1632073,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 美國佬係唔會因為你爆幾塊玻璃而唔過法案 全部都係中美博弈黎 佢要過你殺埋警都一樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:06:01.000Z","msg":"就算係咁，過份裝修依然冇好處<br />\n為爭取支持又好，減低文宣壓力都好<br />\n裝修有明確原則係好事<br />\n<br />\n就好似以武抗暴要出師有名，同埋要對方出手先<br />\n<br />\n有原則先可以正名"},{"pid":"bb89eba54e276a6f1e1e2466d80efbe59a95757d","tid":1632073,"uid":82520,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:07:54.000Z","msg":"btw我知原post主起底鬼鬼地<br />\n但係講嘅野依然有一定參考價值"},{"pid":"dd0c803ad6eff9be3ce43d0083c8fa8acbdc80ff","tid":1632073,"uid":39021,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"192a7b905a37323f2b57b2a8ba5da1b510b8f641","tid":1632073,"uid":73381,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:02:29.000Z","msg":"唔好玩啦 美國佬係唔會因為你爆幾塊玻璃而唔過法案 全部都係中美博弈黎 佢要過你殺埋警都一樣過<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:18:25.000Z","msg":"sorry<br />\n我睇到你咁講好嬲，非常嬲，嬲到想殺人<br />\n但我決定和氣語氣回覆你，因為我真係好想你睇清楚現實<br />\n<br />\n美國係三權互相制衡，司法機關同外交策略無關，不提<br />\n外交事務由行政主導，通常較為現實，以利益權衡為首要考慮，即係你所講既博奕<br />\n對比之下，美國國會更能代表美國國民道德一面，因為國會唔需要好似行政咁多權衡考慮，所以好多時遣責其他國家既聲明，都係由國會發出，行政機關想停都停唔到<br />\n<br />\n你睇唔睇到行政同立法機關最大分別係邊？<br />\n就係立法機關比行政機關更注重道德同形象<br />\n我希望你明白，美國議員為咗形象同選票，佢既行為係一定要乎合相當既道德基准"},{"pid":"bc58ce2de742d5cb47f20d7391307733910e30d7","tid":1632073,"uid":17209,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-10-06T17:20:33.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\"><span style=\"color: red;\">只有民主法案通過，香港政商先有機會重新歸邊，香港人先有機會贏</span></span>"}]}